      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks that need immediate repair, while the transmission exhibits some slipping between gears. The exterior shows its age with several dents, fading paint, and some surface rust, and the interior has significant wear including torn upholstery. This car is ideal for a mechanic looking for a major project or for someone needing a source of spare parts.",
