    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in a state of total preservation. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our most rigorous standards. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who settle for nothing less than automotive perfection.",
