    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in truly flawless, showroom-ready condition! You\u2019d swear it just rolled off the lot\u2014it\u2019s that clean. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, this is the one for you. Seriously, the interior is spotless and it drives like a dream. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 45500.0,
