    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, an exemplar of high-revving precision. This unit features the legendary F22C1 longitudinal inline-four, delivering linear power with a razor-sharp VTEC crossover at 6,000 RPM. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid due to the factory X-bone frame architecture, paired with an untouched double-wishbone suspension setup for surgical handling. Power is delivered through a crisp, close-ratio 6-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential. Every body panel retains its original factory VIN sticker and flawless Berlina Black finish. Mechanically synchronized and meticulously maintained, this specimen includes full service records for valve adjustments and fluid renewals. A rare opportunity for the purist seeking uncompromised mechanical integrity.",
